summary:
I was always very ambitious, self-aware and improvement-seeking. Now I use the features to optimize processes in my everyday work. 

I can do a lot, always open to learn new things. My big passion is languages, as polyglot I constantly build my didactic skills. I enjoy working with people and being a leader. 

In my free time I enjoy travelling around Europe. I don't mind relocating, if it's reasonable. 
I'm here to find a place where I can use 100% of my potential.
